title: HBP - Volume 1 - Issue 01.pdf
description:
Note from the editor

Welcome to all the readers of my very own sustainable technology magazine. As some of you may know I am Andy Mahoney, I run Home Brew Power and up until no it has been a hobby.
You may be asking yourself why I have decided to take the plunge and create a magazine? The truth is that every moment of my life my head is spinning with all the issues of sustainable living, new projects, concepts, what others are doing out there to make a difference to our planets wellbeing.

So it hit me that my heart is not in my 9 to 5 job as a
n electrician. I feel that my heart lies in getting all the exciting content in my head across to other like minded indi-viduals. It is what I want to do, it is what I have always wanted to do.


The dream is alive!

Andy M - Creator Of The HomeBrewPower Magazine & Website

Visit www homebrewpower co uk - Insert Dots ;-)
